OL,3,CLone sailor towed to safety by RNLI
OL,4,Cafter engine failure
OL,6,FA lone sailor was rescued by the RNLI
OL,7,Fafter his engine failed, leaving him
OL,8,Fstuck in rough weather close to busy
OL,9,Fshipping lanes.
OL,11,FThe Hoylake RNLI received reports of a
OL,12,F29ft yacht stuck between the Burbo
OL,13,FOffshore Wind Farm and busy shipping
OL,14,Flanes in the River Mersey on Monday 20
OL,15,FAugust
OL,17,FHoylake RNLI's Shannon class lifeboat
OL,18,FEdmund Hawthorn Micklewood and her
OL,19,Fvolunteer crew launched and soon
OL,20,Farrived on scene within 20 minutes.
