OL,4,Cafter engine failure
OL,6,FWith the vessel unable to get underway
OL,7,For reach safe harbour in enough time
OL,8,Fdue to the rough sea and the ebbing
OL,9,Ftide, it was assessed that the safest
OL,10,Foption was for the lifeboat to take
OL,11,Fthe yacht under tow.
OL,13,FThe yacht was towed through the Rock
OL,14,FChannel by Hoylake RNLI lifeboat and
OL,15,Fwas transferred safely to the New
OL,16,FBrighton RNLI volunteer crew, who
OL,17,Fhelped the casualty to take up the
OL,18,Fmooring.
